::Skulletron::

	Skulletron looks at all the mech fluid.  That must have been some battle.

	"Hey uh, Bloodystrike, when do you think Zardus will come back?  I am
starting to get a craving for war," Skulletron asks, and then grabs his gun
and points it at the roof, feeling pride in himself.  He put his gun back
and waited for an answer.
